<Content>Good value place to stay! I would certainly return to this hotel and recommend it to friends and family.Very pleasant small 2*hotel with 4* value. Exceptionally clean and tidy. Breakfast was adequate and unhurried. Receptionist staff spoke OK english and were very helpful.Hotel California is situated in an ideal location, just off Las Ramblas and next to Placa Reial. Could be a bit noisy but that's what holidays are for.I have read that it is one of a few hotels in Barcelona that is happy to accomodate openly gay couples. 
